text: Dame Laura Rebecca Kenny, Lady Kenny, ( Trott; born 24 April 1992) is an English track and road cyclist. She has won six Olympic medals and is both the most successful female cyclist. She is tied with Charlotte Dujardin as Britain's female Olympian with many medals. == Personal life == She is married to Olympic medalist Jason Kenny. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:British cyclists Category:Olympic gold medalists for Great Britain Category:Olympic silver medalists for Great Britain Category:Sportspeople from Essex
